{
  "text": "Are you saying then there are an infinite number of octaves of densities one through eight? I am wrong. We wish to establish that we are truly humble messengers of the law of one. We can speak to you of our experiences and our understandings and teach, learn in limited ways however we cannot speak in firm knowledge of all the creations. We know only that they are infinite. We assume an infinite number of octaves, however it has been impressed upon us by our own teachers that there is a mystery-clad unity of creation in which all consciousness periodically coalesces and again begins. Thus we can only say we assume an infinite progression, though we understand it to be cyclical in nature, and as we have said, clad in mystery.",
